Package io.openems.common.websocket

Class MyDraft6455

java.lang.Object
org.java_websocket.drafts.Draft
io.openems.common.websocket.MyDraft6455
public class MyDraft6455 extends org.java_websocket.drafts.Draft
This class is basically a copy of the class Draft_6455. The only difference is that it does not throw a IncompleteException internally instead it returns normally in those cases and checks afterwards with an "if" if the result is correct.
